title: Anne's House of Dreams
creator: Lucy Maud Montgomery
description: LibriVox recording of Anne's House of Dreams by Lucy Maud Montgomery. Read by Karen Savage. Anne's story continues with her marriage to Gilbert and their years in the House of Dreams. (Summary by Karen Savage) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; audiobook; anne; fiction
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody:
A beautiful recording. 

Karen Savage is one of LibriVox's best female talents and has improved her style over the years.  Speed and pacing is very good and Karen's youthful voice is the perfect vehicle for this sentimental favourite.

TheBookworm (Manchester, UK)
